                        <interp inst="t18650410-name-93" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY JOHNSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a printer, and carry on business with Mr. Carter at 9, West-street, Soho—I know the defendant—on 20th December, he brought me a manuscript—I afterwards printed this pamphlet by his direction.</p>
